WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:02.480
Hey, Happy Thanksgiving, everybody.

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:04.480
Thank you for joining us.

00:00:04.480 --> 00:00:05.920
Well, praise the Lord.

00:00:05.920 --> 00:00:09.333
I want to give God thanks for all the things that He's done for us.

00:00:09.333 --> 00:00:11.850
I mean, man, God's been good this year.

00:00:11.850 --> 00:00:18.971
You know, if you go back and reflect on all the things the Lord has done, what has He done for you?

00:00:18.971 --> 00:00:21.760
I want you to—it could be something.

00:00:21.760 --> 00:00:26.224
I know the Lord's done something for you this year so far.

00:00:26.224 --> 00:00:36.426
We still have 30-some days left until the first of the year, until January of 2025, but look at what He's done in 2024.

00:00:36.426 --> 00:00:38.506
And what a time in America.

00:00:38.506 --> 00:00:47.220
You know, you can do it wherever you live, just giving God praise and thanksgiving for everything He's done in your life.

00:00:47.220 --> 00:00:51.839
He has been so merciful in so many areas.

00:00:51.839 --> 00:00:59.564
I look back, I mean, just looking back at all of the things He's done this year, you know, with Megan and how far she's come.

00:00:59.564 --> 00:01:19.577
We've had a great year with her, seeing healings come and manifestations of the glory with the outpouring at the Tent Revival, seeing the Shekinah Glory Cloud, going to see Billy Burke and smelling the fragrance of the Holy Spirit—so many amazing things, just supernatural.

00:01:19.577 --> 00:01:29.280
The words that the Lord has given me protected President Trump from the assassination attempts twice, maybe even three times.

00:01:29.280 --> 00:01:33.017
Seeing a Red Wave like the Lord gave us.

00:01:33.017 --> 00:01:53.670
There are so many things that you can be thankful for: that we have a new president coming and helping bring a turnaround to America, and just a lot to be thankful for even going into 2025, regardless of all the rumors of wars and all the things that you see on the news.

00:01:53.670 --> 00:01:57.559
Yeah, there's drama, but there's always something to be thankful for.

00:01:57.559 --> 00:02:00.680
There's always something to give God praise for.

00:02:00.680 --> 00:02:11.120
You know, a lot of what happened with Abraham—one of my favorite verses is that Abraham staggered not at the promise of God through unbelief, but was strong in faith, giving glory to God.

00:02:11.120 --> 00:02:18.274
He gave praise to God even before he saw the full manifestation of what he was believing for.

00:02:19.577 --> 00:02:26.459
Even in the deadness of Sarah's womb, he was thankful, giving glory to God.

00:02:26.459 --> 00:02:30.120
That was him giving praise, being thankful.

00:02:30.120 --> 00:02:37.040
I give You praise, Lord; I thank You for all that You've done, all that You're going to do, and all You continue to do.

00:02:37.040 --> 00:02:42.573
And so, I just take a time, even right now, to say, 'God, thank You.

00:02:42.573 --> 00:02:56.794
' Thank You, Father, for all that You provided: for our clothes, our house, the car we drive, the air we breathe, the sun that shines, the trees that are around the earth.

00:02:57.668 --> 00:03:02.737
Father, for all of the grass and for the water and for all the things that He provided.

00:03:02.737 --> 00:03:04.999
He could have been a really boring God.

00:03:13.799 --> 00:03:15.584
He could have had one kind of tree—it could have been an oak tree or whatever—and that was the only tree He made.

00:03:23.346 --> 00:03:25.1000
He could have made one flower, could have made one bird, but He made all kinds of things for us richly to enjoy.

00:03:27.480 --> 00:03:28.491
Isn't that amazing?

00:03:28.491 --> 00:03:34.519
He made all the different things: all the different kinds of cows, all the different kinds of dogs.

00:03:34.519 --> 00:03:37.454
You may say, 'Well, I don't like that kind of dog,' but He gave you another kind of choice.

00:03:37.454 --> 00:03:41.879
Maybe you like cats; He gave you all kinds of different cats.

00:03:43.639 --> 00:03:49.274
He is so exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

00:03:49.274 --> 00:03:53.045
And there's something—you say, 'I don't have anything to be thankful for.

00:03:53.045 --> 00:03:58.672
' Oh, I guarantee you, if you just stop and think just a little bit, you can think of something.

00:03:58.672 --> 00:04:01.089
I have something to be thankful for.

00:04:01.089 --> 00:04:19.171
And it's just like—when you give God praise and you give God worth and you take the time to give Him an offering of thanksgiving in every area of your life, it brings the glory down, because when praises go up, blessings come down.

00:04:19.588 --> 00:04:22.498
He is worthy of it.

00:04:23.327 --> 00:04:26.405
He is the El Elyon, the Most High.

00:04:26.405 --> 00:04:29.480
He's the Jehovah Jireh, He's everything that I need.

00:04:29.480 --> 00:04:34.863
He has it, and He's made it for us richly to enjoy.

00:04:36.044 --> 00:04:37.270
I love that scripture.

00:04:37.270 --> 00:04:38.919
And so, you know what?

00:04:38.919 --> 00:04:46.644
You may say, 'Well, I'm not all the way where I need to be in overcoming,' but I saw a little bit of change this year.

00:04:46.644 --> 00:04:48.485
I saw a little bit.

00:04:48.485 --> 00:04:57.800
I may not have my full manifestation of what I've been believing for, but I saw some change.

00:04:57.800 --> 00:05:03.650
Noah released the dove, and it came back with just a little olive branch.

00:05:03.650 --> 00:05:12.160
But Noah knew that was a sign that the flood was over, and he gave God praise for it.

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:21.902
Just that little olive leaf, that little twig in its mouth, represented that the flood was over and that God doesn't dangle a carrot.

00:05:21.902 --> 00:05:29.885
Like Billy Burke said to us, God doesn't dangle a carrot and heal partway just to lead you on.

00:05:29.885 --> 00:05:32.268
God's a full manifestation God.

00:05:32.268 --> 00:05:36.639
So if you've seen something, there's hope in that.

00:05:37.080 --> 00:05:40.457
There's hope in that little bit of a turnaround.

00:05:40.457 --> 00:05:50.552
That's that olive leaf that you've got today to say, 'God, I have something to be thankful for today,' regardless of how much more you have to go.

00:05:52.280 --> 00:05:57.680
You got the olive leaf; it was the sign that the flood was over.

00:05:58.040 --> 00:06:05.759
In your life, you may have no pain in your elbow, and it may just be a little spot in your elbow that doesn't have pain.

00:06:06.119 --> 00:06:12.775
Give God praise for that no pain in that elbow, or that little toe that doesn't hurt anymore.

00:06:16.234 --> 00:06:27.880
You may go, 'Oh, but everything else hurts so bad,' but give God praise for it because that's the sign that the flood is turning around in your life.

00:06:27.880 --> 00:06:31.570
Believe that today.

00:06:31.570 --> 00:06:38.280
Reach out today and give God praise for every single thing He's done.

00:06:38.280 --> 00:06:47.120
It may just be, 'My toenail doesn't hurt today, Lord,' but it's a sign that the flood is subsiding in your life.

00:06:49.554 --> 00:06:59.639
That storm that was sent to try to kill, steal, and destroy you and pull you down all the way under—there's a sign of relief today.

00:06:59.639 --> 00:07:05.519
That's what you have to grab onto: those glimmers of hope.

00:07:05.519 --> 00:07:11.866
My hope is built on nothing less than Jesus' blood and His righteousness.

00:07:11.866 --> 00:07:21.927
I believe with all my heart that today our olive leaf is here, and we give God praise for that olive leaf.

00:07:21.927 --> 00:07:30.295
I tell Diana all the time we see the change and the tide is changing with Megan on a day-to-day basis.

00:07:38.709 --> 00:07:39.220
Regardless of if she may have a bad day the next day, we say, 'Nope, we're still standing on the good day.

00:07:39.220 --> 00:07:43.679
' We had several good days this year.

00:07:48.330 --> 00:07:52.120
We had some bad days, but we're not focused on the bad days; we're focused on the good days.

00:07:52.120 --> 00:08:01.194
Because you've got to give God praise for every single good day and say, 'You know what?

00:08:01.194 --> 00:08:09.604
We may have had a bad day today, but we're going to have a good day tomorrow.

00:08:09.604 --> 00:08:14.526
' Regardless of your circumstances, joy comes in the morning.

00:08:14.526 --> 00:08:17.280
That's exactly right.

00:08:20.685 --> 00:08:30.120
I believe that we can call those things that be not as though they were by speaking to our circumstances to change.

00:08:34.088 --> 00:08:34.457
You may be all alone in this holiday season.

00:08:35.563 --> 00:08:44.866
You may be sitting there on your couch and you're all by yourself and you're thinking, 'Man, nobody cares about me.

00:08:44.866 --> 00:08:51.484
' But Diana and I are here and we're here for you.

00:09:06.503 --> 00:09:06.965
We're praying for you.

00:09:06.965 --> 00:09:12.073
Know that we're lifting you up before the Father.

00:09:12.073 --> 00:09:14.100
That hit me—somebody's really struggling.

00:09:14.100 --> 00:09:16.883
I felt that intercession hit me.

00:09:16.883 --> 00:09:27.279
Somebody's out there believing for someone to be their friend, and I just want to let you all know we're your friend.

00:09:27.279 --> 00:09:31.040
We're in your corner; we're believing with you.

00:09:31.040 --> 00:09:37.120
We stand with you when you feel, 'I don't have anybody out there that loves me.

00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:41.177
Why am I even on this earth?

00:09:41.177 --> 00:09:45.675
God doesn't care about me; He's forgotten about me.

00:09:45.675 --> 00:09:46.386
I'm broken.

00:09:46.386 --> 00:09:48.780
I have no friends, no wife, no husband.

00:09:48.780 --> 00:09:51.120
All my relatives have passed on.

00:09:51.120 --> 00:09:52.992
I have no kids.

00:09:52.992 --> 00:09:55.218
I'm all alone on this holiday season.

00:09:55.218 --> 00:09:57.319
Why am I still here?

00:09:57.319 --> 00:10:04.653
' But God has a plan for you, and this will be the best year you've ever lived so far.

00:10:04.653 --> 00:10:07.584
In 2024, we're going to find some friends.

00:10:07.584 --> 00:10:17.459
Say that: 'I'm going to make myself friendly, and I'm going to find some friends.

00:10:17.459 --> 00:10:24.800
' The year is not over; you don't have to be down and out or sad.

00:10:24.800 --> 00:10:34.440
It's a time to have joy in your heart, a smile on your face, and a song in your heart, because Jesus loves you.

00:10:34.440 --> 00:10:45.079
Just like we say every day: put a smile on your face and a song in your heart; Jesus loves you.

00:10:45.079 --> 00:10:48.670
You know, that came from my dad.

00:10:48.670 --> 00:11:04.576
My mom had a lot of hard times whenever they were going through a lot of poverty, and my mom would fuss around the house a lot.

00:11:04.576 --> 00:11:19.670
My dad would always tell my mom, 'You need to put a smile on your face and a song in your heart,' because she would be so fussy about it.

00:11:29.670 --> 00:11:29.980
That came right up out of him.

00:11:29.980 --> 00:11:34.675
As a kid, that's always been in my heart; it's always stirred me.

00:11:34.675 --> 00:11:40.040
But that came out of my dad because we had such a hard time growing up.

00:11:40.040 --> 00:11:43.514
They struggled a lot, but we made it through.

00:11:44.568 --> 00:11:51.576
I met Diana, and it's been the greatest thing of my life, just going through life with her.

00:11:56.480 --> 00:12:04.800
And yet we've had our challenges, and yet it seemed like I left Mom and Dad's mess and we had our own mess started up.

00:12:04.800 --> 00:12:08.095
But God has been faithful, hasn't He, babe?

00:12:08.095 --> 00:12:08.565
Yes.

00:12:08.565 --> 00:12:12.190
And He's brought us through some trying times.

00:12:12.190 --> 00:12:16.575
But it wasn't something that we got overnight.

00:12:16.575 --> 00:12:27.200
We had to believe and keep on keeping on, regardless of what we saw in the natural.

00:12:27.200 --> 00:12:36.079
It felt like we were never going to get out of it—poverty and lack.

00:12:36.079 --> 00:12:46.989
But with the creative ideas to do eBay and Poshmark and Facebook Marketplace, thinking, 'How are we going to get out of this?

00:12:46.989 --> 00:12:53.249
' when you're going from paycheck to paycheck and you think, 'I don't have any ideas.

00:12:53.249 --> 00:13:05.885
' But God, who is rich in mercy, will give you a creative idea to do something different and then give you favor with thrift store owners.

00:13:05.885 --> 00:13:06.622
Who knew?

00:13:15.247 --> 00:13:16.587
You walk in there and start talking to somebody, and you let that favor of God shine on you.

00:13:16.587 --> 00:13:28.123
You don't go in there and start witnessing and hitting them in the head with the Bible.

00:13:28.123 --> 00:13:30.867
You let your light shine through your eyes.

00:13:30.867 --> 00:13:34.399
You just go in there—man, God's good.

00:13:34.399 --> 00:13:43.432
You just have that attitude of, 'I know who I am in Christ, and I'm going to display Jesus today.

00:13:43.432 --> 00:13:46.147
' He blesses the fruit of your hands.

00:13:46.147 --> 00:13:51.1000
It's like my boss always used to tell me: 'Preach the gospel always, and sometimes use words.

00:13:51.1000 --> 00:14:00.544
' I thought that always stuck out to me when he said that to me: preach the gospel always, and then sometimes use words.

00:14:00.544 --> 00:14:07.444
Why are you going to preach the gospel if you're not using words?

00:14:07.444 --> 00:14:09.303
It's in your life.

00:14:30.170 --> 00:14:30.575
It's what you display on a day-to-day basis to everybody around you.

00:14:30.575 --> 00:14:35.399
Who are you when nobody else is looking?

00:14:35.399 --> 00:14:39.371
Especially the Christian people at church—who are you in the real world?

00:14:39.371 --> 00:14:40.565
Let your light shine.

00:14:40.565 --> 00:14:48.745
Showing up and showing Jesus, and not just always preaching at people.

00:14:48.745 --> 00:14:50.199
Show the love of God to people.

00:14:50.199 --> 00:14:58.069
Yeah, even when we're in a restaurant or whatever, I will clean up our messes.

00:14:58.069 --> 00:15:05.799
People notice things like that; it's your light shining.

00:15:05.799 --> 00:15:14.199
If you see a piece of trash on the floor and you pick it up...

00:15:14.199 --> 00:15:30.249
yeah, taking the buggy, like Joyce Meyer says—taking the buggy to the stall instead of letting it ding somebody else's car when you drive off.

00:15:38.589 --> 00:15:39.177
It's just taking the extra mile of excellence.

00:15:39.177 --> 00:15:43.491
Showing excellence in everything you do.

00:15:43.491 --> 00:15:48.920
Being like Daniel—Daniel was a man of excellence in everything he did.

00:15:48.920 --> 00:15:52.609
We need to be like Jesus, too.

00:15:52.609 --> 00:16:10.800
But the Bible talks about how Daniel was a man of excellence, and I just want to show that excellence that Jesus shows up and shows off in my life just by me being me.

00:16:10.800 --> 00:16:20.874
It's like when I go and get our mail at the post office box—I just love on people.

00:16:20.874 --> 00:16:24.815
If I go and get a coffee somewhere, I just love on them.

00:16:24.815 --> 00:16:26.560
'Hey, how's your day?

00:16:26.560 --> 00:16:30.524
' And just talk to them.

00:16:30.524 --> 00:16:40.439
They start to wonder, especially if you have a good attitude and you display joy and love.

00:16:40.439 --> 00:16:42.239
Joy is contagious.

00:16:42.239 --> 00:16:48.776
People right now are hurting, and they're looking for authentic Christians.

00:16:48.776 --> 00:17:17.610
As we see things in the news and on social media right now that try to tarnish Christianity and ministries, it's time that we show up and show people we have Jesus, regardless of what they hear in the news or what's going to break on CNN or Fox or any of these other places.

00:17:17.610 --> 00:17:21.974
When they say there's a scandal, show Jesus.

00:17:28.486 --> 00:17:33.714
You have a platform with the person at Walmart, with your local grocery store, and they see you are authentic, not fake.

00:17:33.714 --> 00:17:34.177
I love that.

00:17:34.177 --> 00:17:54.291
That's the ultimate Christian in my opinion: somebody who's just in the ditches, in the trenches, cleaning the church, helping out in the nursery, being an usher year after year with no recognition.

00:17:54.291 --> 00:18:07.553
If it wasn't for you ushering and being a door greeter, would that person who came that wasn't saved feel welcome?

00:18:07.553 --> 00:18:15.580
It's the small things that make the unbeliever see a relationship with the Lord and find it.

00:18:15.580 --> 00:18:19.359
It's that one word of kindness that changes people.

00:18:25.742 --> 00:18:26.191
So, be thankful today.

00:18:26.191 --> 00:18:29.290
Be thankful for everything.

00:18:42.610 --> 00:18:48.533
I pray that this blessed you today.

00:18:48.533 --> 00:18:52.501
We're going to pray with you now.

00:19:03.365 --> 00:19:14.260
I want you to agree with me that every need you have is met, that we take authority over this war, that there are no major wars coming, that we would have peace, and that God would give us an extended time of Grace.

00:19:14.260 --> 00:19:17.260
That's what He said: pray for this.

00:19:17.260 --> 00:19:29.022
Pray that President Trump has supernatural wisdom in leading this country, that when he is inaugurated on January 20th, we will have a supernatural turnaround.

00:19:29.022 --> 00:19:45.782
God, who is rich in mercy, shows up and shows off in a major way because His people who are called by His name are praying and turning from their wicked ways.

00:20:00.359 --> 00:20:00.719
Father, we just thank You, Lord, for every single person who's represented here today.

00:20:15.975 --> 00:20:16.300
They may be alone, they may be thinking, 'I don't have anybody,' but God, You're there too.

00:20:16.300 --> 00:20:23.994
As we lift them up to You, we lift up their hearts and that loneliness.

00:20:23.994 --> 00:20:35.840
Holy Spirit, we ask You to go right where they are right now and fill them with Your Shekinah Glory and Your presence.

00:20:37.613 --> 00:20:42.194
In the presence of Jehovah God Almighty, Prince of Peace, troubles vanish, hearts are mended.

00:20:52.491 --> 00:20:53.023
We thank You, Father, that You're mending the hearts and that in that presence, there's peace.

00:21:11.697 --> 00:21:12.028
I pray a supernatural peace over their life today, over their minds today, that they realize that Jesus loves them.

00:21:12.028 --> 00:21:22.830
I pray, Father, for them to find friends at church and people who would care for them.

00:21:39.739 --> 00:21:40.029
I thank You, Father, as they sow love, they will reap it a hundredfold return—a supernatural seed time and harvest concerning the love of God.

00:21:40.029 --> 00:21:48.640
I thank You, Lord, that You're encouraging them today, that they have no yoke and no burden.

00:21:48.640 --> 00:21:53.045
They have joy unspeakable and full of glory.

00:21:53.045 --> 00:22:02.959
Their minds are renewed to the Word of God, and they realize how much You love them.

00:22:16.640 --> 00:22:17.750
I thank You, Father, for every single person represented here who is believing for an unsaved loved one, for a child that's strayed, whom they haven't heard from during this holiday season.

00:22:17.750 --> 00:22:26.131
Father, I thank You, Lord, that we call those kids home in the name of Jesus.

00:22:26.131 --> 00:22:41.191
Holy Spirit, we ask You to put it on their hearts right now to call their mother or their father or their loved ones and check up with them.

00:22:45.988 --> 00:22:47.223
I thank You, Father, that they would just come home and restore the family.

00:22:47.223 --> 00:23:01.599
Father, I thank You, Lord, this is a time of great restoration—restoration of all things over our families and our unsaved loved ones.

00:23:07.145 --> 00:23:10.679
We call them born again, we call them filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit.

00:23:10.679 --> 00:23:17.069
Father, we ask that You would open the eyes that Satan has blinded.

00:23:17.069 --> 00:23:25.240
We call their eyes to be enlightened right now in the name of Jesus.

00:23:26.413 --> 00:23:33.860
I speak to their ears to hear You, Lord, right now.

00:23:33.860 --> 00:23:50.360
All the demonic spirits that have been lying to them and speaking perverse things—we command them to go now in Jesus' name.

00:23:50.360 --> 00:23:58.070
We speak to their ears to pop open; they would hear Your voice, Lord.

00:23:58.070 --> 00:24:05.444
Be saved, be born again, turn from your wicked ways.

00:24:05.444 --> 00:24:16.024
I thank You, Lord, that they would hear You.

00:24:16.024 --> 00:24:27.371
We call forth the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever known, in the name of Jesus.

00:24:27.371 --> 00:24:32.427
We're calling those souls in.

00:24:32.427 --> 00:24:40.506
We thank You, Lord, that the laborers are coming, the harvesters are coming.

00:24:40.506 --> 00:24:53.377
I thank You, Lord, that the harvesters are bringing forth the harvest, uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

00:24:53.377 --> 00:25:05.273
There is one last call for a mighty move of God, one last call for healing before Your Son's return.

00:25:26.147 --> 00:25:26.480
I thank You, Lord, that You're shaking the churches all around the world, waking up all of the people who are asleep.

00:25:26.480 --> 00:25:55.200
Shaking the churches and the pulpits so that the great move of God would flow like a mighty rushing wind, bringing forth the great harvest and the light of God would shine in the name of Jesus.

00:25:55.200 --> 00:26:05.133
Even among the Latter-day Saints, Father, that they would turn and have a revelation knowledge of who You are at a greater level.

00:26:05.133 --> 00:26:14.830
Father, I thank You, Lord, that we come against false religion and all kinds of demonic spirits.

00:26:14.830 --> 00:26:20.667
We thank You, Lord, for an authentic move of God in the churches.

00:26:20.667 --> 00:26:29.826
Thank You, Father, that You would show us where we are in error in our ways.

00:26:30.587 --> 00:26:34.568
I thank You, Lord, that You're exposing false doctrines and false religion.

00:26:34.568 --> 00:26:50.805
I thank You, Lord, that You expose this, that the eyes of their understanding would be enlightened in the name of Jesus.

00:26:53.214 --> 00:26:56.106
We plead the blood of Jesus Christ over every single person represented here today.

00:27:15.764 --> 00:27:16.102
Jesus has a plan for every single one of us.

00:27:16.102 --> 00:27:32.840
Let there be a mighty rushing wind of Your Spirit upon this earth one last time, just like it was in Acts chapter 2.

00:27:33.075 --> 00:27:42.805
Father, I thank You, Lord, for a fresh touch, a fresh presence, a fresh anointing on every single person.

00:27:42.805 --> 00:27:45.374
Fan the flame, oh God!

00:27:45.374 --> 00:27:48.840
Stir in them right now in Jesus' name.

00:27:48.840 --> 00:27:56.520
Shaking off all the bondage, taking off the scales of religion and perverse, reprobate thinking.

00:27:56.520 --> 00:28:03.171
Bringing them close to the fire and the heart of God.

00:28:04.422 --> 00:28:14.011
That they repent and turn from their wicked ways, that they humble themselves and pray and seek Your face, Lord.

00:28:14.011 --> 00:28:25.760
This is a time like never before to run back to the altars and repent, to bring the glory back into our churches.

00:28:25.760 --> 00:28:37.434
Shake the religious spirits out of the churches and bring forth fresh fire, a fresh presence on Your churches, Lord.

00:28:37.434 --> 00:28:41.234
Shaking the seeker-friendlies, shaking the lukewarm.

00:28:58.679 --> 00:28:59.366
We thank You, Father, for Your creative miracles and for healings.

00:29:12.260 --> 00:29:12.640
We call forth explosions of Your glory inside of these churches.

00:29:14.784 --> 00:29:24.640
Father, when the pastor preaches, let the presence of God weigh so strong that there would be a holy hush upon the congregation—a holy glory throughout the congregation.

00:29:24.640 --> 00:29:37.839
As that comes on that congregation, Lord, a great repentance, a great holiness, a great outcry of Your Spirit would stir up inside of them.

00:29:37.839 --> 00:29:45.310
They would say, 'I need more of You and less of me.

00:29:45.310 --> 00:29:53.011
' For judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:30:08.799 --> 00:30:12.590
Father, fix what's broken in our churches first, and then I thank You, Lord, that the greatest harvest of souls would come forth out of the darkness.

00:30:12.903 --> 00:30:22.954
I call forth from the north, south, east, and west—all through the Buddhist communities, the Muslim communities, and all of the false religions.

00:30:22.954 --> 00:30:31.399
I say, in the name of Jesus, for their eyes to be enlightened with light.

00:30:31.399 --> 00:30:39.266
I thank You for angelic visitations and manifestations of glory.

00:30:39.266 --> 00:30:46.953
Use the person who's just in the marketplace, working on their jobs.

00:30:49.645 --> 00:30:56.669
Father, when they lay hands on the sick, just like You said in Your Word, they would recover.

00:30:56.669 --> 00:31:04.367
I thank You, Father, for this last call, for this last outpouring.

00:31:04.367 --> 00:31:07.822
We call forth Elon Musk today.

00:31:07.822 --> 00:31:13.564
We say: will you pray for him for 20 days?

00:31:20.288 --> 00:31:22.606
That Elon Musk would be radically born again, filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit.

00:31:26.339 --> 00:31:31.079
I call forth laborers across his path to show and share the love of God to Elon Musk.

00:31:31.079 --> 00:31:47.166
I thank You, Father, that people of character are put around him to snatch him right out of the hand of darkness.

00:31:47.166 --> 00:31:54.039
I thank You, Father, that Donald Trump has a fire in him.

00:31:54.039 --> 00:31:58.440
God, I pray for gasoline on that supernatural fire in Jesus' name.

00:31:58.440 --> 00:32:01.733
Stir and stir, Holy Spirit!

00:32:01.733 --> 00:32:19.022
Stir in that family with great divine protection according to Psalm 91, that a thousand shall fall at their side and ten thousand at their right hand, but nothing shall come nigh them.

00:32:19.022 --> 00:32:23.600
No plots or plans of the wicked will be successful.

00:32:23.600 --> 00:32:33.212
We call forth a divine angelic visitation of protection over every one of the family members, over the Vice President, and over the President.

00:32:34.427 --> 00:32:43.620
And we thank You, Lord, for the ones we have in there now—I thank You, Lord, that they don't do anything else corrupt while they're in there.

00:32:43.620 --> 00:32:51.609
I thank You, Father, that there is no more trying to bring down America.

00:32:51.609 --> 00:32:53.884
No more of it, in Jesus' name.

00:32:53.884 --> 00:33:02.466
With war and sending long-range missiles, we call peace over Russia, Ukraine, and Europe in Jesus' name.

00:33:09.755 --> 00:33:10.020
That President Trump will not be known as a wartime president.

00:33:21.719 --> 00:33:22.059
We have peace, an extended four years of grace and blessing until 2028.

00:33:22.059 --> 00:33:26.069
I thank You, Father, that You're coming soon.

00:33:26.069 --> 00:33:27.845
Jesus is coming.

00:33:33.337 --> 00:33:36.585
We should be busy about doing what the Father's called us to do—occupy until He comes.

00:33:36.585 --> 00:33:39.439
Being bold and radical about the Father's business.

00:33:39.439 --> 00:33:45.159
Just like Paul Revere in the night, saying, 'The British are coming!

00:33:45.159 --> 00:33:53.440
' Father, we would stand in the darkness on our horse, saying, 'Jesus is coming!

00:33:53.440 --> 00:33:54.834
Jesus is coming!

00:33:54.834 --> 00:34:09.139
' Calling forth the men and women and women getting ready for the soon return of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:34:09.139 --> 00:34:14.191
Because there is a great battle ahead to win the lost.

00:34:14.191 --> 00:34:17.270
When the anointing comes on me, I yell.

00:34:17.270 --> 00:34:24.239
Thank You, Father, for a supernatural move of Your presence around the world one last time.

00:34:24.239 --> 00:34:29.851
Thank You, Lord, for protecting the Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade today.

00:34:29.851 --> 00:34:34.080
Thank You, Lord, that no calamity comes nigh.

00:34:34.080 --> 00:34:46.879
Thank You, Lord, that nothing happens at the Rockin' New Year's Eve, and that tomorrow, whenever people are Black Friday shopping, no weapon formed against the people will prosper.

00:34:50.911 --> 00:34:51.168
I thank You, Lord, that people are protected.

00:34:51.168 --> 00:34:59.196
Lord, we give You all the glory, honor, and praise for it in the mighty name of Jesus.

00:34:59.196 --> 00:34:59.538
Amen.

00:34:59.538 --> 00:35:02.800
Well, thank you for coming and praying with me today.

00:35:02.800 --> 00:35:13.589
I know it's a shorter video, but I wanted to make it where you could go and spend time with your families.

00:35:13.589 --> 00:35:22.000
If you don't live in America and you don't celebrate Thanksgiving, celebrate it where you are.

00:35:22.000 --> 00:35:23.244
Be thankful today.

00:35:23.244 --> 00:35:25.910
If you're new here, we pray every day.

00:35:25.910 --> 00:35:29.640
Diana and I are praying together, believing with you for your healings, for anything that you have need of.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Nothing's too big for God.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
All things are possible to him who believes.

